A '''bedroom''' can be made in a [[player-owned house]] using the [[Construction]] skill. Players must have at least level 20 Construction to be able to make a bedroom. To hire a [[servant]], there must be at least two bedrooms with beds within the player's house. It costs {{NoCoins|10000|c}} to build.

There are seven different types of [[hotspot]] the player can build on:
*[[Bed space]]
*[[Corner space]]
*[[Curtain space]]
*[[Dresser space]]
*[[Fireplace space]]
*[[Rug space]]
*[[Wardrobe space]]

The bedroom has 2 non-parallel doors. This makes it an efficient corner room.

